        {
            "_id": "LXvqvVhorWXVewtI",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Twist Time",
            "sort": 700000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Xae attempts a ghostly hand strike. If she hits, she inflicts damage as normal, but the target struck must also attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:30] save (the target takes a -2 penalty to this saving throw if the strike was a critical hit).</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 1 round as the rest of reality seems to speed up.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature becomes decrepit from unnatural aging. It is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 2}, and as long as it has the slowed condition, it is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 2} as well.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but the creature feels death knocking on the door-it is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Doomed]{Doomed 1} as long as it remains slowed by Twist Time.</p>"
                },
